# Merging on the 'State' column
merged_data <- combined_df %>%
   left_join(df_states, by = c("State" = "state"))


merged_data <- merged_data %>%
  mutate(PopupInfo = paste(State, "<br/>Individuals Affected: ", IndividualsAffected))


aggregated_data <- merged_data %>%
  group_by(State, latitude, longitude) %>%
  summarise(TotalAffected = sum(IndividualsAffected, na.rm = TRUE), 
            .groups = 'drop') # Ensure Latitude and Longitude are included for mapping


#Obtained from chatgpt
aggregated_data <- aggregated_data %>%
  mutate(PopupContent = paste("<strong>State:</strong>", State, 
                              "<br/><strong>Total Individuals Affected:</strong>", TotalAffected))

leaflet(data = aggregated_data) %>% 
  addTiles() %>%
  addCircleMarkers(
    lng = ~longitude, 
    lat = ~latitude, 
    popup = ~PopupContent,
    clusterOptions = markerClusterOptions()
  ) %>%
  setView(lng = -98.5795, lat = 39.8283, zoom = 4)
